{"title":"EL基本使用","date":"2019-04-28T09:04:21.000Z","link":"2019/04/28/Java Web/EL","tags":["Java Web"],"categories":["Java Web"],"updated":"2019-10-17T06:46:59.179Z","content":"  <a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h2 id=\"EL表达式使用\">EL表达式使用<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/EL#EL表达式使用\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"简介\">简介<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/EL#简介\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li><p>概念： Expression Language</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>作用： 简化替换 jsp中的java代码编写</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>语法：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$&#123; Expressioin&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n<li><p>注意</p>\n<p>jsp默认支持el表达式。如果忽略的话</p>\n<ol>\n<li>page指令中 isELIgnored=”true” 忽略全部</li>\n<li>\\${EL} ：忽略当前的页面表达式</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"使用\">使用<a href=\"2019/04/28/Java Web/EL#使用\"></a></h3><ol>\n<li><p>运算</p>\n<ol>\n<li>算数运算符 ： + - * / div % (mod)</li>\n<li>比较运算符 :  &gt; &lt; &gt;= &lt;= == !=</li>\n<li>逻辑运算符 ： &amp;&amp; || !</li>\n<li>空运算符  :  用于集合 字符串等的使用</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li><p>获取值</p>\n<p>语法：</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>使用</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$&#123;域名称.键名&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  &lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\"> request.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"alan \"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    session.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"a\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">  %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">  $&#123;requestScope.name&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  $&#123;sessionScope.name&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tpageContext.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"page\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\trequest.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"request\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tsession.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"session\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tapplication.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"application\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t按普通手段取值&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;%= pageContext.getAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>)%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;%= request.getAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>)%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;%= session.getAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>)%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;%= application.getAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>)%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;br&gt;使用EL表达式取出作用域中的值&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t$&#123; pageScope.name &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t$&#123; requestScope.name &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t$&#123; sessionScope.name &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t$&#123; applicationScope.name &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><p>获取对象中的值 对象</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">      </span><br><span class=\"line\">   User user = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> User();</span><br><span class=\"line\">   user.setName(<span class=\"string\">\"zhangsa\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   user.setAge(<span class=\"number\">12</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">      </span><br><span class=\"line\">   request.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"u\"</span>, user);</span><br><span class=\"line\"> %&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">      </span><br><span class=\"line\">      </span><br><span class=\"line\"> $&#123;requestScope.name&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> $&#123;sessionScope.name&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> $&#123;u.age&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> $&#123;u.name&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><p>数组 同理list</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t\tString [] a = &#123;&quot;aa&quot;,&quot;bb&quot;,&quot;cc&quot;,&quot;dd&quot;&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t\tpageContext.setAttribute(&quot;array&quot;, a);</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t使用EL表达式取出作用域中数组的值&lt;br&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">   \t\t$&#123;array[0] &#125; , $&#123;array[1] &#125;,$&#123;array[2] &#125;,$&#123;array[3] &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li><p>集合map</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;!-- </span><br><span class=\"line\">$&#123;域名称.键名.key名称&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$&#123;域名称.键名.[<span class=\"string\">\"key名称\"</span>]&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">--&gt;\t</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tMap map = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> HashMap();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tmap.put(<span class=\"string\">\"name\"</span>, <span class=\"string\">\"zhangsna\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tmap.put(<span class=\"string\">\"age\"</span>,<span class=\"number\">18</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tmap.put(<span class=\"string\">\"address\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"北京..\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tmap.put(<span class=\"string\">\"address.aa\"</span>,<span class=\"string\">\"深圳..\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\treqeuest.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"map\"</span>, map);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">$&#123;map.name &#125; , $&#123;map.age &#125; , $&#123;map.address &#125;  , $&#123;map[<span class=\"string\">\"address.aa\"</span>] &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li><p>empty判段</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight c\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;%</span><br><span class=\"line\">List <span class=\"built_in\">list</span> = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> ArrayList&lt;&gt;();</span><br><span class=\"line\">request.setAttribute(<span class=\"string\">\"list\"</span>,<span class=\"built_in\">list</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">%&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">$&#123;<span class=\"keyword\">not</span> empty <span class=\"built_in\">list</span>&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<pre><code>虚拟目录的获取jsp页面中\n</code></pre>   <figure class=\"highlight jsp\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$&#123;pageContext.request.contextPath&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"RequestR以及response基础","link":"2019/04/28/Java Web/Request Response"},"next":{"title":"栈的典型应用——计算后缀表达式","link":"2019/04/15/DataStructure/Stack"},"plink":"http://zqynn.github.io/2019/04/28/Java Web/EL/","toc":[{"title":"EL表达式使用","id":"EL表达式使用","index":"1","children":[{"title":"简介","id":"简介","index":"1.1"},{"title":"使用","id":"使用","index":"1.2"}]}],"copyright":{"link":"<a href=\"http://zqynn.github.io/2019/04/28/Java Web/EL/\" title=\"EL基本使用\">http://zqynn.github.io/2019/04/28/Java Web/EL/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}